column8: 7SjW0EGhVM8Khairuddin: Najib's sons participate in official visit to China?Published on May 14, 2017More questions have been raised on the participation of the Prime Minister's son Norashman and stepson Riza Aziz in official government working visits abroad.Khairuddin Abu Hassan said chief secretary to the government Ali Hamsa should explain the reasons for their presence at a function Najib attended in China.
